  "description": "I have this lineage of theory that goes roughly:\nliberal ontologizing induces genring induces ontogenring attributing is an ontogenric act attributing induces ontogenric entitlement and ontogenric anticipation the condition of saturation induces destabilization ontogenring narrativizes saturation-induced destabilization as collapse \u0026hellip;Maza has distracted me\u0026hellip; \u0026hellip;something about affect theory \u0026hellip;thus, californication? ",
